title: MS Exchange: Information Store Performance
agents: windows
catalog: app/exchange
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the performance/load of the core data storage repository.
 It measures the average latency of requests.

 {WARN} and {CRIT} thresholds can be configured, defaults are based of
 suggestions published on microsofts technet.

inventory:
 One service is created for each store. Stores can be mailboxes or public folders.
